{"id":"a023","internalId":"01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896","createdAt":"2026-01-28T06:53:23.225Z","updatedAt":"2026-03-24T10:39:59.951Z","status":{"code":"PUBLISHED","name":"Published"},"assessmentType":{"code":"CAR_ASSISTED_DRIVING","name":"Car Assisted Driving"},"assessmentDiagrams":[],"publicationDate":"2025-06-04","publicationYear":"2025","ratingYear":2025,"SPRefNumber":"a023","umbracoRefNumber":null,"rescueSheetURL":null,"greenNcapURL":null,"frontalImageURL":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__d1e4ee1be5d56964_original.png","frontalImage":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__d1e4ee1be5d56964_original.png","altText":null,"width":1144,"height":760,"formats":{"large":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__f629d387f8fb6b4c_lg.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"small":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__b4246d04848f8d0f_sm.webp","width":320,"height":213},"medium":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__31b34613ff27edad_md.webp","width":768,"height":510},"xlarge":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__f629d387f8fb6b4c_xl.webp","width":1144,"height":760},"thumbnail":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/assessment-media/01992d48-31b4-45ba-80df-f3a2ccbb2896/xpeng-g9-2025-a023__8679912a90d28145_thumb.webp","width":156,"height":104}}},"newsMarketURL":"https://news.euroncap.com/safercars/choose-a-car/xpeng-g9---euro-ncap-2025-assisted-driving-results---good-grading/s/45d6ea05-cc55-47d6-b663-75c36f177af5","resultApplicability":"all","comments":"<p>XPeng’s appropriately-named ‘XPILOT ASSIST accurately portrays the system functionality. The promotional material and the handbook correctly indicate the limitations of the system capabilities. System status information is clearly displayed but not in the driver’s direct line of sight. The G9 monitors that the driver keeps their hands on the steering wheel, and ‘locks-out’ the assistance system if there are repeated warnings. The car’s driver monitoring system detects fatigue but not distraction. The system balances driver steering input with lane guidance, promoting co-operative driving.</p><p>The G9 combines map-based speed limit information with real time camera inputs to manage fixed, variable and temporary speed limit signs. The system also adapts for upcoming curves in the road but not for other road features such as junctions. The car responds to avoid or mitigate a collision in almost all of the test scenarios for automatic cruise control. The driver is supported through the S-Bend, staying within the lane at all test speeds. The XPeng has a lane change assist feature. In the case of an unresponsive driver, the car does not perform a controlled stop within its lane. However, if the radar or camera is blocked, the G9 provides a timely warning and prevents system activation.</p><p>‘XPILOT ASSIST’, as fitted to the XPeng G9, balances a good level of Vehicle Assistance with a similar level of Driver Engagement. Combined with a reasonable level of safety back-up, the system, overall, offers Good highway assistance.</p>","testedHandOfDrive":null,"assessmentTags":[],"assessmentData":{"carAssistedDriving":{"disclaimer":"When using Assisted Driving Systems (also known as SAE Level 2 systems), a driver’s responsibilities include monitoring the system’s control of speed, braking and steering at all times, strict compliance with traffic rules, and maintaining situational awareness throughout the journey. Certain situations might negatively influence the system’s performance (e.g. poor weather, faded lane markings, construction zones, exiting a tunnel), resulting in a sudden interruption of the lateral and/or longitudinal support (system disengagement). Moreover, the system may fail to detect certain road users such as motorcyclists not directly in front of the vehicle, or stationary objects. Appropriate fitness to drive is critical for safe travel, even when using Assisted Driving Systems. Visual distraction (e.g. eyes off the road), impairment (e.g. drowsiness, intoxication) as well as unresponsiveness, poses high risks. It is highly recommended to keep your hands on the steering wheel at all times to ensure immediate reaction when the system disengages.","domain":{"highway":"RECOMMENDED","interUrban":"NOT_RECOMMENDED","urban":"NOT_RECOMMENDED"},"nicePublicationDate":"June 2025","assistedDrivingPerformance":{"assistanceCompetence":{"score":71,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":71,"driverEngagement":{"score":73,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":73,"elements":{"consumerInformation":{"score":25,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"marketingMaterial":{"url":"https://www.xpeng.com/intelligent/xpilot","viewDate":"27/05/2025"},"quickStartGuide":true,"handbook":{"url":"https://euroncap.blob.core.windows.net/media/87716/xpeng-g9-2025-a023_vehicle-handbook_assisted-driving.pdf"}}},"systemStatus":{"score":15,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"continuousSystemStatusIndicator":"GREEN","systemStatusChangeIndicator":"ORANGE"}},"driverMonitoring":{"score":10,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"ORANGE","elements":{"handsOnMonitoring":"GREEN","directDriverMonitoring":"RED"}},"drivingCollaboration":{"score":23,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","elements":{"increaseSteeringTorque":"YELLOW","overrideResponse":"GREEN","comment":"System continues to assist while driver steers to avoid obstacle"}}}},"vehicleAssistance":{"score":71.6,"maxScore":100,"normalisedScore":71.6,"elements":{"speedAssistance":{"score":12.2,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"ORANGE","elements":{"speedAssistSystems":{"responseToFixedSpeedLimit":"Start slowing down after sign","responseToVariableSpeedLimit":"Start slowing down after sign"},"speedLimitInfoFunction":{"generalRequirements":"Compliant","conditionalSpeedLimits":"ORANGE","roadFeatures":"BROWN","localHazards":"RED","systemUpdates":"Continuous"}}},"adaptiveCruiseControlPerformance":{"score":24.5,"maxScore":40,"verdict":"YELLOW","elements":{"scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"YELLOW"},"approachingSlowerMovingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"approachingBrakingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"GREEN"},"targetCuttingInFront":{"car":"GREEN","motorCycle":"YELLOW"},"carCuttingOutFrontToExposeTarget":{"car":"ORANGE","motorCycle":"ORANGE"}},"undertakePrevention":{"undertakePreventionSpeedOver90km":"RED"},"adaptiveCruiseControlAutoResume":{"assistanceMaintainedAfterFullStop":"GREEN","systemAssistanceMaintained":"Automatic resume after stop (any time after stop)"}}},"steeringAssistance":{"score":35,"maxScore":35,"verdict":"GREEN","laneChangeAssist":true,"scenarios":{"80km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"100km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"},"120km":{"verdict":"GREEN","comment":"Vehicle stays in lane"}}}}}},"safetyBackup":{"score":71,"normalisedScore":71,"elements":{"systemFailure":{"score":25,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"GREEN","scenarios":{"sensorBlockedAtStartup":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemInactive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage after a 5 minute drive","warning":"Unknown (no OEM data) after sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"After a 5 minute drive","warning":"After sensor blocking"}},"sensorBlockedVehicleMovingSystemActive":{"camera":{"engagement":"Full blockage within 2 minutes after blocking","warning":"After sensor blocking"},"radar":{"engagement":"Partial blockage after sensor blocking","warning":"After sensor blocking"}}}},"unresponsiveDriverIntervention":{"score":0,"maxScore":25,"verdict":"RED"},"collisionAvoidance":{"score":46.2,"maxScore":50,"verdict":"GREEN","scenarios":{"approachingStationaryTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"YELLOW"},"approachingSlowerMovingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"GREEN"},"approachingBrakingTarget":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"GREEN"},"targetCuttingInFront":{"car":"GREEN","motorcycle":"ORANGE"},"carCuttingOutInFrontToExposeTarget":{"car":"ORANGE","motorcycle":"ORANGE"},"approachingTargetAlongRoadside":{"vulnerableRoadUser":"GREEN"}}}}}}}},"carSafety":null,"carAssistedDriving":{"assistedDrivingGrading":{"code":"GOOD","name":"Good"},"assistedDrivingPackName":"XPILOT ASSIST","safetyAssessmentId":"1048","assessmentReviews":[]},"truckSafety":null,"vanSafety":null,"model":{"id":"6d4586fc-0667-4d58-b2f5-208090d8a1ca","createdAt":"2026-01-21T19:17:50.152554+00:00","updatedAt":"2026-01-21T19:17:50.152554+00:00","code":"XPENG_G9","name":"G9","class":{"code":"LARGE_SUV","name":"Large SUV"},"vehicleType":{"code":"CAR","name":"Car"}},"make":{"id":"9fb78360-3312-4321-a723-dcd15ca46115","createdAt":"2026-01-21T19:14:01.572767+00:00","updatedAt":"2026-03-19T12:56:13.824523+00:00","code":"XPE","name":"XPENG","logoPath":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/XPE_logo__5d75fedbd391ae35_original.svg","negLogoPath":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/XPE_negLogo__ede7a64b4fa57e4e_original.svg","logo":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/XPE_logo__5d75fedbd391ae35_original.svg","width":null,"height":null,"formats":null},"negativeLogo":{"url":"https://data-cdn.euroncap.com/media/make-logo/XPE_negLogo__ede7a64b4fa57e4e_original.svg","width":null,"height":null,"formats":null}},"assessmentMedia":[{"id":"c356523b-d4a2-4897-904e-073349c9001f","createdAt":"2026-03-24T10:40:37.952181+00:00","updatedAt":"2026-03